data.text:
GOLDBERG, Cecil Verner Edward

Suddenly in Bracebridge on Monday, January 23, 2023 at the age of 63. Cec, loving father to Trevor (Julie), Christina, Amanda (Ryan), Rebecca and Victoria. Grandpa will be sadly missed by Jadyn, Josie, Brielle, Hailey, Keegan and Tryson. Dear brother to Justina (Jon Budney), Christina (Len Page), and Tammy Craig (Donna). Predeceased by his father Vern and mother Annabelle and her husband Allan. He will be sadly missed by many nieces, nephews, extended family and friends.
